COLLECTOR OF INTERNAL REVENUE, H. I. Hinds, v. George P. LIVERMORE, Executor. No. 4798. United States Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Feb. 8, 1954. Fred M. Mock, U. S. Atty., Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellant. Hatcher, & Bond, Chickasha, Okl., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Chief Judge, and KNOUS, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed pursuant to stipulation.
